targets.query:
from(bucket: "hb9cu")
  |> range(start: v.timeRangeStart, stop: v.timeRangeStop)
  |> filter(fn: (r) => r["_measurement"] == "measurement")
  |> filter(fn: (r) => r["_field"] == "snr")
  |> group(columns: ["call"])
  |> count()
  |> group()
  |> yield(name: "beacon")

from(bucket: "hb9cu")
  |> range(start: v.timeRangeStart, stop: v.timeRangeStop)
  |> filter(fn: (r) => r["_measurement"] == "measurement")
  |> filter(fn: (r) => r["_field"] == "snr")
  |> group(columns: ["call"])
  |> count()
  |> group()
  |> yield(name: "beacon")

from(bucket: "hb9cu")
  |> range(start: v.timeRangeStart, stop: v.timeRangeStop)
  |> filter(fn: (r) => r["_field"] == "snr")
  |> group(columns: ["call"])
  |> sort(columns:["_time"])
  |> aggregateWindow(every: 30d, fn: max)
  |> group(columns: ["monitor_id"])
  |> keep(columns: ["_value", "geohash", "call", "monitor_id", "mhz"])
  |> map(fn: (r) => ({r with name: r.call +" (" + r.mhz + "mhz)"}))
  |> yield(name: "beacon")

panels.title: Highest SNR/Band for selected TIme range

targets.query:
duration = if (uint(v: v.timeRangeStop) -  uint(v: v.timeRangeStart)) > 3600*24*1000*1000*1000*2 then 1d else 1h

from(bucket: "hb9cu")
  |> range(start: v.timeRangeStart, stop: v.timeRangeStop)
  |> filter(fn: (r) => r["_measurement"] == "measurement")
  |> filter(fn: (r) => r["_field"] == "snr")
  |> group(columns: ["call"])
  |> aggregateWindow(every:duration, fn: max)
  |> map(fn: (r) => ({_value:r._value, _time:r._time, _field:r._field}))
  |> group(columns: ["_time"])
  |> count()
  |> group()
  |> map(fn: (r) => ({_value:r._value, _time:r._time, _field: "Beacons heard"}))
  |> keep(columns: ["_value", "_time", "_field"])
  |> yield(name: "beacon")
